docs.text:
Welcome to MkDocs


For full documentation visit 
mkdocs.org
.


Commands




mkdocs new [dir-name]
 - Create a new project.


mkdocs serve
 - Start the live-reloading docs server.


mkdocs build
 - Build the documentation site.


mkdocs help
 - Print this help message.




Project layout


mkdocs.yml    # The configuration file.
docs/
    index.md  # The documentation homepage.
    ...       # Other markdown pages, images and other files.

docs.text:
LD_LIBRARY_PATH and LD_RUN_PATH






LD_LIBRARY_PATH
 Specifies the directories that are to be searched for libraries at run time.






LD_RUN_PATH 
Specifies the directories that are to be searched for libraries at both link and run time.
docs.title: LD_RUN_PATH
